title: [The Black Rose, Engineering]
description: Approaching the engineering section, the lengths of crimson-varnished wood give way to lightless blocks of crystal.  An enclosure of precious metals fans out around a pulsating hexagonal blue crystal, the source of an ethereal pulse bathing the chamber in blue-white luminescence.  Faint, haunting notes pour forth from the depth of the crystal in a strange and unending song.
room.location: The Black Rose, inside the elven fortress of Ta'Vaalor
